datasource.query:
SELECT
	'',
	REGEXP_EXTRACT(labels, r'\|machine_type:(.*?)\|') AS machine_type,
	REGEXP_EXTRACT(labels, r'\|cloud:(.*?)\|') AS cloud,
	%%EXPRESSION%% AS number
FROM
	[{{ dataset_name }}.{{ table_name }}]
WHERE
	timestamp >= TIMESTAMP_TO_SEC(DATE_ADD(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), -3, 'MONTH')) AND
	product_name = 'PerfKitBenchmarker' AND
	test = 'scimark2' AND
	metric = 'Composite Score' 
GROUP BY
	machine_type,
	cloud
ORDER BY
  number ASC;
